title: Tiffany Haddish is the Last Black Unicorn
description:
Tiffany Haddish is so undeniably funny that she was putting Quincy Jones in his place at 15 years old. This week Claire and Ashley are running through the pages of her life in absolute awe of her ability to make literally everything funny.  


Get 15% off your first set of sheets at bollandbranch.com promo code WORM at checkout.
